-- MOVES-U.S. Bank Wealth Management names Dominic Cotrano wealth management adviser 
-- 
-- Tue Oct 28, 2014 01:30PM EDT
-- None



Oct 28 (Reuters) - U.S. Bank Wealth Management, a unit of U.S. Bancorp <USB.N>, appointed Dominic Cotrano as wealth management adviser for the private client reserve of U.S. Bank in Chicago.

Prior to joining the private client reserve, Cotrano was a wealth management senior adviser and private banker with MB Financial.